A precept fra the Governour to the Maister of Sempille

Gubernator

Traist cousing we commend ws hertlie to yow Forsamekile as the Blak- freris of Glasgw hes bene heir at ws and hes schevin to ws how thair con- vent and place is langtyme bipast infeft in ane yerelie almouse of sex bollis vittale of the hovse of Derlyng and hes beine ay continualie and thank- fullie pait and yerelie ansuerit thairof till now lait of few yeris bigane We pray yow effectuouslie that ye cause mak thame reddy payment of the said almouse of yeris bigane and sielik in tymes cuming conforme to thair said infeftment quhilk we haue seine and causit consider sa that the puire religiouse men be nocht fravdit in our tyme bot rathar helpit to thair almouse This ye caus to be done as ye will do ws plesour And God haue yow in kepinge At Paslay the xiij day of August

James G

[In dorsa] To our traist cousing the Master Sempill
